                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable N</hi> 345.) The prisoner was given into my custody—I said he was charged with robbing the prosecutor—he said it was no robbery—I found on him this razor, and wig, and some cuttings of hair.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I had the screw-driver down stairs; the razor was sent to the grinder's, and generally the master's name is put on the razors, as this is.</p>
